   The president urged Indonesian authorities ''to bring those
responsible to justice, to disarm and disband the militias and to
take all necessary steps to insure the safety of those continuing
to work on humanitarian goals there.''
</P>
<P>
   His speech was part of the U.N. Millennium Summit.
</P>
<P>
   In Washington, Pentagon spokesman Kenneth Bacon said Defense
Secretary William Cohen will visit Indonesia later this month to
meet with government and military officials.
