Dow Ends Down 51; Nasdaq Gains 85
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- High-tech stocks rebounded today after a two-day downturn,
while blue chips fell following another spate of corporate earnings warnings.
The Nasdaq composite index ended the day up 85.01 at 4,098.25, and the Dow Jones
industrial average was down 50.77 at 11,259.87.
</P>
