   HOUSTON (AP) -- Chris Truby singled home the go-ahead run in the eighth
inning, leading Scott Elarton and the Houston Astros over the Florida Marlins
7-3 tonight. Elarton (16-5) won for the 12th time in 14 decisions since June 22.
He pitched eight innings, giving up three runs and seven hits.
</P>
